areas
  - id
  - Name
  - Banner image url
  - map image url
  - Bond level bonus servants (foreign keys?)
  - point/fights (foreign keys?) * may be story only
  - rewards for clearing
  - requirements (foreign key for other areas?)
  - period (for events)
  - shop (for events)
  - Sum of fights rewards (optional - nice to have)

fights/points
  - ap cost
  - map point image url
  - available npcs (foreign key to servants?)
  - PSs
  - drops (foreign key for items?)
  - Battles (list of enemies): lvl, class and hp - (foreign key for enemies?)
  - completion rewards - may be servant skill/np upgrade if interlude
  - Exp rate (optional) - bond and xp

items
  - id
  - Name
  - image url
  - drop map (foreign key?)
  - drop enemy (foreign key to enemies)
  - description
  - type
  - CE bonus (FK?)

enemy
  - Name
  - traits
  - drops (FK to items?)
  - image url
  - fights/points it appears (FK)
  - maps (FK to fights/points)

skill_enhancements
  - servant (FK)
  - item (FK)
  - servant skill level (2 ~ 10)
  - quantity